*pecl-apcu_bc-1.0.3 (26 Feb 2016)

  26 Feb 2016; Brian Evans <grknight@gentoo.org> +pecl-apcu_bc-1.0.3.ebuild:
  Version bump; rename extension file

  In order to consistently load apc_bc, install it as bc_apc.so
  This only requires a simple rename instead of hacking the eclass
  to provide a different ini file name which does not always work.

